Running Code
When you click the Render button a document will be generated that includes both content and the output of embedded code. You can embed code like this:


Code
1 + 5


[1] 6


You can add options to executable code like this


[1] 4


The echo: false option disables the printing of code (only output is displayed).

title: Analysis 2
text:
Code
data("population")




Code
filter(population, country %in% c("China", "India", "Great Britain", "United States of America")) %>% 
  ggplot() + geom_line(aes(year, population, group = country, color = country)) + 
    scale_y_log10(labels = scales::number_format(scale = 1e-6, suffix = "M"))
